%e9%b3%b3%e7%b0%a1%2c355%2c20221013%2c2/pdf"},"JID":"FSEV,111,鳳簡,355,20221013,2","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"鳳簡","JNO":"355","JDATE":"20221013","JTITLE":"清償借款"}